title: Vic's Pizzeria
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Italian, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Pizzas by the slice or made-to-order, calzones, salads, and desserts. Vegans get a choice of Ana's Vegan Sauce (nutritional yeast, tahini, and garlic yumminess) or vegan white sauce instead of cheese on pizzas or in calzones, and there are usually vegan slices available. Lots of toppings including two types of tofu, mango chutney, and spinach. Whole wheat crust available. Will accommodate requests. Olympia beer on tap as well as other beers and wines. Coffees available with soy or rice milk. Relaxed atmosphere, non-smoking. Free Wi-fi.
